title: Janos Meny - Personal Website
snippet: I'm Janos Meny, a mathematician who turned programmer, specializing in geometry processing, optimization, and computer graphics. I studied mathematics at the University of Bonn, focusing on algebraic geometry in my bachelor's and PDE-constrained optimization in my master's.
